<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Foodalyze Wireframe</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #FAF3DD; /* Oatmeal Beige */
            color: #3A2C2A; /* Dark Walnut */
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #F4A261; /* Golden Honey */
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .container {
            width: 90%;
            margin: 20px auto;
        }
        .hero {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px;
            background-color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        .hero button {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #52796F; /* Soft Pine Green */
            color: white;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .features {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
        .feature-box {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            width: 30%;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #3A2C2A; /* Dark Walnut */
            color: white;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">Foodalyze - Scan & Eat Smart
    </div>
    
    <div class="container">
        <div class="hero">
            <h1>Find Out if Your Food is Healthy</h1>
            <p>Scan the barcode on any food package to analyze its ingredients.</p>
            <button>Scan Now</button>
        </div>

        <div class="features">
            <div class="feature-box">
                <h3>Scan</h3>
                <p>Use your camera to scan food barcodes instantly.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-box">
                <h3>Analyze</h3>
                <p>Get a detailed breakdown of ingredients and nutrition.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-box">
                <h3>Choose Wisely</h3>
                <p>Discover healthier alternatives and make better food choices.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">&copy; 2025 Foodalyze | Eat Smart, Live Healthy</div>
</body>
</html>